---
title: Curried Turkey Tortillas with yoghurt and sweet chilli drizzle
description: The warmed tortillas in this recipe are piled high with some really great ingredients. Spiced turkey is complemented with crunchy salad and off topped with a dollop of cooling yoghurt.
